      "span_text": "The first series of inbred lines (inbred series A) was obtained from a diploid clone 97H32-6 (composed of 75% cultivated and 25% wild germplasm with 100% cultivated cytoplasm), which was self-compatible due to the function of the Sli gene originally derived from a self-compatible variant of S. chacoense"
